  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to evaluate the molecular mechanism underlying the erythroid response
      observed in some patients with myelodysplasia, myelofibrosis and aplastic anemia treated
      with Deferasirox or Deferoxamina.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Recruiting</overall_status>
  <start_date>May 2013</start_date>
